data.description: Welcome home to your beautiful house on a tranquil 3 acres. From the moment you walk up to the house, you can envision sipping coffee on the front porch. As you step inside, you will be greeted with beautiful flooring and lots of natural light. Walking through the house is easy with this layout. Imagine preparing meals in your fully equipped kitchen as you interact with family in the living room. Great open concept. All bedrooms are upstairs and amply sized. The largest ensuite is your oasis after a busy day. Spending time outdoors in your backyard will be your new daily routine. Plenty of trees for privacy too. You will love what this home offers!
